room_title: Escape room "Museum Heist" by Breakout Games - Chattanooga in Chattanooga
review: I visited breakout games with my mother and adult siblings for my mother's birthday. We did the museum heist room. It was fun and a lot more challenging than I anticipated! We also had reserved a time slot and were taken into our game on time. The whole thing takes about an hour. I can't wait to go back and try the other challenges!
